        - Project name title is hidden if the summary is shown since it's already there
        - Added milestone date fields for studio multi-round contests.
   
    Version 1.0.2 (Cockpit Pipeline Release Assembly 2 - Capacity) Change notes:
        - Removed pre calculated start date
        - Removed restriction for start date to begin 14 days from now
        - Changed the way restricted dates are handled for start date (pipeline web service is now used)

    @author pulky
    @version 1.0.2
    @since 1.0
-->
